                  </persName>
            . I live with Mr. Paine, a pawnbroker in Bow-street near Bloomsbury, (the shift, two aprons, and four handkerchiefs produced,) these I took in of the prisoner at the bar in her name at different times, (deposed to by prosecutrix.)</p>
               <p>Prisoner's defence.</p>
               <p>I beg the court will be as merciful as they can.</p>
